  "body": "        A non-local node that is not operated by a provider is probably more of an unconventional niche setup overall.\r\n\r\nHowever, this should be better supported.\r\n\r\nThere should be a flag to opt out of ratelimit prevention I think, will add this\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @mattsse in https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/issues/3648#issuecomment-1311962646_\r\n      \r\n\r\nPerhaps `--no-rate-limits` would be the appropriate flag here\r\n",
